# Canonical person nodes referenced by works, references, and lesson usages.
#
# Keep one `person:<slug>` node per real person and reuse it from the other TTL fragments
# instead of duplicating author data inline. Store only stable identity metadata here
# (`givenName`, `familyName`, and optional public profile URLs). Publishers, venues, and
# documentation sites belong in `02-organizations.ttl`, not in this file.
@prefix schema: <https://schema.org/> .
@prefix dibs: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/vocab#> .
@prefix ref: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/ref/> .
@prefix person: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/person/> .
@prefix org: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/org/> .
@prefix work: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/work/> .
@prefix usage: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/usage/> .

